## Scaling Challenges by Rank

As the party advances through ranks, scale challenge difficulty:

| Party Rank | Standard TN | Hard TN | Story Stakes |
|------------|-------------|---------|--------------|
| Novice | TN 8 | TN 10 | Local threats, personal stakes |
| Seasoned | TN 10 | TN 12 | Regional threats, community stakes |
| Veteran | TN 10 | TN 12 | Kingdom-wide threats, political stakes |
| Heroic | TN 12 | TN 14 | Continental threats, legendary stakes |
| Legendary | TN 12 | TN 14 | World-ending threats, mythic stakes |

**Note:** After characters reach the +5 modifier cap (timing varies by build), challenges scale through complexity and stakes rather than raw difficulty numbers. Scale TNs based on party modifier, not rank.

